Due to the non-stop harassment to us devs on the r/jailbreak subreddit from users and other social medias about 20mb of depends, calling yt reborn a virus and a death threat found in my mail (Ryan H), I have decided to cancel YouTube Reborn myself, sorry, I just can't take it anymore 
 Thank you to the r/jailbreak mods and admins for doing there best to stop it, they have been removing multiple posts/comments of it over the past week. Its just been to much for me to handle and it hasn't stopped.
